  <entry>
    <title>使用说明</title>
    <link href="/mafei.github.io/2026/05/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/"/>
    <url>/mafei.github.io/2026/05/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本博客基于 <strong>Hexo</strong> 框架 + <strong>Fluid</strong> 主题搭建，部署于 <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>。本文介绍博客的使用方法，方便你快速上手。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="文章存放位置"><a href="#文章存放位置" class="headerlink" title="文章存放位置"></a>文章存放位置</h2><p>所有文章以 Markdown 格式存放在 <code>source/_posts/</code> 目录下。</p><h2 id="创建新文章"><a href="#创建新文章" class="headerlink" title="创建新文章"></a>创建新文章</h2><p><strong>方式一：命令行</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npx hexo new post <span class="hljs-string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会自动生成带 Front-matter 的 <code>.md</code> 文件。</p><p><strong>方式二：手动创建</strong><br>在 <code>source/_posts/</code> 下新建 <code>.md</code> 文件，需包含 Front-matter。</p><h2 id="文章格式示例"><a href="#文章格式示例" class="headerlink" title="文章格式示例"></a>文章格式示例</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">---<br>title: 文章标题<br>date: 2026-05-21 23:30:00<br>tags:<br><span class="hljs-bullet">  -</span> 标签1<br><span class="hljs-bullet">  -</span> 标签2<br>categories:<br><span class="hljs-bullet">  -</span> 分类名称<br>cover: /img/cover.jpg        # 封面图（可选）<br><span class="hljs-section">excerpt: 文章摘要文字          # 摘要（可选）</span><br><span class="hljs-section">---</span><br><br>正文内容，支持完整 Markdown 语法。<br><br><span class="hljs-section">## 二级标题</span><br><br><span class="hljs-strong">**加粗**</span>、<span class="hljs-emphasis">*斜体*</span>、<span class="hljs-code">`行内代码`</span><br><br><span class="hljs-section">### 代码块</span><br><br><span class="hljs-code">```javascript</span><br><span class="hljs-code">console.log(&quot;Hello World&quot;);</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h3><table><thead><tr><th>列1</th><th>列2</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>A</td><td>B</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a></p><h3 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h3><p><img src="/mafei.github.io/img/image.jpg" alt="描述文字"></p><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gherkin"><br><span class="hljs-comment">## Front-matter 字段说明</span><br><br>|<span class="hljs-string"> 字段 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 必填 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 说明 </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">------</span>|<span class="hljs-string">------</span>|<span class="hljs-string">------</span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `title` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ✅ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 文章标题 </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `date` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ✅ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 发布日期 </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `updated` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ❌ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 更新日期 </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `tags` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ❌ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 标签（数组格式） </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `categories` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ❌ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 分类（数组格式） </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `cover` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ❌ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 封面图路径 </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string"> `excerpt` </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ❌ </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 文章摘要 </span>|<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">## 博客名称修改</span><br><br>编辑根目录的 `_config.yml`：<br><br>```yaml<br>title: 博客标题              <span class="hljs-comment"># 浏览器标签显示</span><br>subtitle: &#x27;副标题&#x27;           <span class="hljs-comment"># 首页副标题</span><br>author: 作者名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>导航栏标题编辑 <code>_config.fluid.yml</code>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">navbar:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">blog_title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;导航栏显示的文字&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置文件位置"><a href="#配置文件位置" class="headerlink" title="配置文件位置"></a>配置文件位置</h2><table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>用途</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>_config.yml</code></td><td>站点主配置（标题、URL、部署等）</td></tr><tr><td><code>_config.fluid.yml</code></td><td>主题配置（导航栏、背景、评论等）</td></tr><tr><td><code>scaffolds/post.md</code></td><td>新文章模板</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npx hexo new post <span class="hljs-string">&quot;标题&quot;</span>     <span class="hljs-comment"># 新建文章</span><br>npx hexo new draft <span class="hljs-string">&quot;标题&quot;</span>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 新建草稿</span><br>npx hexo server              <span class="hljs-comment"># 本地预览</span><br>npx hexo generate            <span class="hljs-comment"># 构建</span><br>npx hexo deploy              <span class="hljs-comment"># 部署到 GitHub Pages</span><br>npx hexo clean               <span class="hljs-comment"># 清理缓存</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="部署流程"><a href="#部署流程" class="headerlink" title="部署流程"></a>部署流程</h2><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs verilog">写文章 → hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">generate</span> 构建 → hexo deploy 部署 → GitHub Pages 自动更新<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>源码分支：<code>main</code></li><li>部署分支：<code>gh-pages</code></li></ul><p>修改后执行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git add -A &amp;&amp; git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;更新&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; git push origin main<br>npx hexo clean &amp;&amp; npx hexo generate &amp;&amp; npx hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>更多配置请参考 <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">Hexo 文档</a> 和 <a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/">Fluid 主题文档</a>。</p>]]></content>
    
    
